                    <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d12">
                      Decorative designs:
                      <locus target="#1r #9r #32r #45v #61v #70r #96v #108r #115v #140r #150r #160r #165r #172v" facs="003 011 034 048 064 072 099 110 118 142 152 162 167 175">fols. 1r, 9r, 32r, 45v, 61v, 70r, 96v, 108r, 115v, 140r, 150r, 160r, 165r, 172v</locus>, ornamental band with the names of the months are written in negative space;
                      in the style of the government scriptorium of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5226haylase">Ḫāyla Śǝllāse I</persName>;
                      multiple full stops are used as section dividers throughout.</decoNote>
